snippet.title: Belonging - First Teaser (2022)
snippet.description:
Dive into the abandoned estate of the Entelecism Cult and reveal their darkest secrets. 
Find out about the cult member's stories and steal their most valuable  posessions.
But make sure you're not taking away any evidence. 

Wishlist now on Steam: https://bit.ly/BLNGSteam

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/farbspiel_games
